  "title": "BIM Modeler/ Engineer (Structural)",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>Construction industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>BIM Modeller </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li>\n  <li><strong>Position:</strong> BIM Modeler</li>\n  <li><strong>Location:</strong> Redhill</li>\n  <li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 5.5 days, Office Hours (Saturday only when necessary)</li>\n  <li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Basic + Bonus</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop 3D models and prepare shop drawings for authority submission and construction purposes using BIM software</li>\n  <li>Update 3D models based on the latest project information and ensure accuracy of drawings</li>\n  <li>Monitor, identify, and report design clashes to the Project Design Team</li>\n  <li>Support the Project Design Team in managing RFIs and technical clarifications</li>\n  <li>Ensure timely submission of drawings according to project schedules</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess a Degree in Civil Engineering and minimum 3 years of relevant experience in the local construction industry (experience with contractor firms preferred)</li>\n  <li>Proficient in BIM software such as Revit (Architecture, MEP, Structure), Tekla, and MicroStation (AECOsim)</li>\n  <li>Hands-on experience in preparing shop drawings for submission and construction</li>\n  <li>Must possess prior modeling experience in both Architectural and Structural disciplines.</li>\n  <li>Able to start immediately or in short notice.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Click the APPLY button, or</li>\n  <li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p>\n<p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
